   <sect2 role="installation">
      <title>Installation de Kcalc</title> 
      
      <para>
         Installez <application>Kcalc</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes: 
      </para> 
      
<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$KDE4_PREFIX \
      -DKDE_DEFAULT_HOME=.kde4 \
      -DSYSCONF_INSTALL_DIR=/etc/kde4 \
      .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>
      
      <para>
         Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur the <systemitem class="username"> root
         </systemitem>&nbsp;:  
      </para> 
      
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install</userinput></screen>
      
   </sect2>
   
